                        The National Institute of Nutrition and Seafood Research
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                
                <p>The National Institute of Nutrition and Seafood Research in Bergen serves in an advisory capacity to the fisheries authorities, the Norwegian Food Safety Authority and the fishing industry on issues concerning nutrition and food safety. The institute also carries out research on nutrition and related subjects.
</p>
                
                
